      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project with tons of potential? This car has a lot of character and is ready for a new owner who isn't afraid to roll up their sleeves! While it shows significant wear and will require some mechanical and cosmetic TLC to get back to its best, it offers a fantastic and affordable entry point into this model. It's the perfect opportunity for a DIY enthusiast to breathe new life into a classic workhorse!",
